<p>The following email notifications are sent to customers when they perform certain actions in a TitleLeaf site.</p>

<ul>
<li>
<p>Upon creating a user account, the user is sent confirmation:</p>
<p><img src="https://assets.titleleaf.com/guide/mail-account-confirmation.png" alt="Titleleaf Mailer Account Confirmation" /></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Upon submitting an order, the customer is sent confirmation:</p>
<p><img src="https://assets.titleleaf.com/guide/mail-order-confirmation.png" alt="Titleleaf Mailer Order Confirmation" /></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Upon releasing an order that contains PDFs or EPUBs, the customer is sent notification:</p>
<p><img src="https://assets.titleleaf.com/guide/mail-downloads-available.png" alt="Titleleaf Mailer Downloads Available Notification" /></p>
</li>
</ul>
